%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20(Not-So-)Hidden%20Agenda%20Behind%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98400%20Paar%E2%80%99%20Slogan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F20123532%2FIMG_2186.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELeaders%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20have%20been%20claiming%20that%20they%20will%20win%20more%20than%20400%20(370%20BJP%20%2B%2030%20allies)%20seats%20in%20the%20forthcoming%20parliamentary%20elections%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20This%20is%20not%20based%20on%20any%20psephological%20analysis%20but%20purely%20propagated%20for%20political%20reasons.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJustifying%20this%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Echar%20sau%20par%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99%20(400%2B)%20slogan%2C%20Karnataka%20BJP%20MP%20Anantkumar%20Hegde%20explained%20the%20need%20for%20such%20a%20figure.%20As%20per%20him%2C%20the%20party%20intends%20to%20change%20the%20Constitution%2C%20for%20which%20two-thirds%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20majority%20is%20needed.%20%E2%80%9CModi%20ji%20said%20that%20we%20need%20to%20secure%20more%20than%20400%20seats%20this%20time.%20Why%20400%3F%20We%20currently%20have%20a%202%2F3%20majority%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20but%20we%20lack%20the%20same%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20where%20our%20majority%20is%20lesser.%20Additionally%2C%20we%20lack%20the%20required%20majority%20in%20the%20state%20governments%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-mp-says-partys-400-seat-goal-for-2024-is-so-it-can-change-constitution%5C%22%3EHegde%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20we%20are%20to%20make%20amendments%20to%20the%20Constitution%2C%20like%20the%20ones%20Congress%20made%2C%20twisting%20the%20fundamental%20principles%20of%20the%20Constitution%20and%20introducing%20provisions%20and%20laws%20that%20oppressed%20Hindus%2C%20then%20this%20majority%20won%E2%80%99t%20suffice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20distanced%20itself%20from%20this%20statement%20of%20the%20sitting%20MP%2C%20as%20if%20they%20do%20not%20really%20approve%20it.%20There%20are%20some%20reports%20saying%20he%20may%20even%20be%20denied%20a%20ticket%20as%20a%20consequence.%20Whether%20he%20is%20denied%20a%20ticket%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOzopdMHpBTc%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20ground%20or%20not%2C%20one%20thing%20is%20certain%20%E2%80%93%20the%20BJP%20has%20no%20aversion%20to%20such%20statements.%20This%20MP%20had%20said%20the%20same%20thing%20in%202017%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DOzopdMHpBTc%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhen%20he%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20a%20Union%20minister%20in%20the%20BJP%20government.%20He%20was%20duly%20given%20a%20ticket%20in%20the%202019%20general%20elections%20by%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20statement%20of%20the%20BJP%20MP%20that%20he%20needs%20400%20seats%20to%20change%20the%20constitution%20is%20a%20public%20declaration%20of%20the%20hidden%20agenda%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ENarendra%20Modi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20his%20%E2%80%98Sangh%20parivar%E2%80%99.%20The%20ultimate%20goal%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20is%20to%20destroy%20Baba%20Saheb%E2%80%99s%20Constitution.%20They%20hate%20justice%2C%20equality%2C%20civil%20rights%20and%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fwatch-congress-launches-nyay-geet-featuring-rahul-gandhi-ahead-of-lok-sabha-elections-101710037070786.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Rahul%20Gandhi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20wrote%20in%20Hindi%20on%20X%20(formally%20Twitter).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20former%20Congress%20president%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-gandhi-reacts-to-bjp-mps-constitution-400-seats-remarks-pm-modis-hidden-agenda-101710058422017-amp.html%3Futm_campaign%3Dfullarticle%26utm_medium%3Dreferral%26utm_source%3Dinshorts%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealso%20alleged%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Cby%20dividing%20society%2C%20restricting%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20crippling%20independent%20institutions%2C%20they%20want%20to%20turn%20India%E2%80%99s%20great%20democracy%20into%20a%20narrow%20dictatorship%20by%20conspiring%20to%20eliminate%20the%20opposition%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20a%20twin%20track%20strategy%20to%20undermine%20the%20democratic%20values%20of%20our%20Constitution.%20Its%20parent%20organisation%2C%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS)%2C%20opposed%20the%20Constitution%20right%20from%20the%20beginning.%20After%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20came%20into%20being%2C%20the%20RSS%E2%80%99s%20unofficial%20mouthpiece%20%3Cem%3EOrganiser%3C%2Fem%3E%20wrote%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6In%20our%20constitution%2C%20There%20is%20no%20mention%20of%20that%20unique%20constitutional%20development%20in%20ancient%20bharat.%20To%20this%20day%20his%20laws%20as%20enunciated%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Emanusmriti%3C%2Fem%3E%20excite%20the%20admiration%20of%20the%20world%20and%20elicit%20spontaneous%20obedience%20and%20conformity.%20But%20to%20our%20constitutional%20pundits%20that%20means%20nothing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftake-nothing-for-granted-not-even-the-constitution%5C%22%3E%20Take%20Nothing%20for%20Granted%2C%20Not%20Even%20the%20Constitution%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20as%20part%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20in%201998%2C%20one%20of%20the%20first%20things%20it%20did%20was%20to%20appoint%20a%20commission%20to%20review%20the%20Constitution.%20However%2C%20the%20Venkatchaliah%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20report%20could%20not%20be%20undertaken%20for%20implementation%20as%20there%20was%20a%20severe%20opposition%20to%20any%20tampering%20with%20our%20Constitution.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESubsequently%2C%20when%20K.%20Sudarshan%20became%20the%20chief%20of%20the%20RSS%20in%202000%2C%20he%20frankly%20stated%20that%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20is%20based%20on%20Western%20values%20so%20it%20should%20be%20replaced%20by%20one%20based%20on%20Indian%20holy%20books.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESudarshan%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Constitution%20was%20of%20no%20use%20for%20the%20people%20of%20the%20country%20as%20it%20was%20based%20on%20the%20Government%20of%20India%20Act%20of%201935%20%E2%80%A6We%20need%20not%20fight%20shy%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwocircles.net%2F2007jun08%2Fconstitution-root-cause-countrys-ills-rss-chief.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealtering%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20constitution%20completely%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%202014%2C%20when%20the%20BJP%20returned%20to%20power%2C%20the%20preamble%20of%20the%20cCnstitution%20and%20the%20use%20of%20%E2%80%98secular%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98socialist%E2%80%99%20have%20remained%20a%20point%20of%20contention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20too%20long%20ago%2C%20chief%20of%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20economic%20advisory%20council%2C%20Vivek%20Debroy%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fbibek-debroy-article-for-new-constitution-pm-panel-says-not-our-view-8897462%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehad%20also%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20called%20for%20a%20new%20Constitution.%20Then%20too%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20had%20officially%20distanced%20himself%20from%20the%20comments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20voices%20of%20major%20stature%20from%20within%20the%20BJP%20as%20well%20as%20state%20officials%20keep%20making%20these%20controversial%20statements%2C%20officially%20the%20BJP%20or%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20makes%20a%20show%20of%20distancing%20itself%20from%20such%20utterances.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20as%20the%20BJP%20completes%20a%20decade%20of%20being%20in%20power%2C%20what%20has%20it%20done%20to%20the%20core%20value%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20%E2%80%93%20democracy%20and%20equality%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20far%20as%20democracy%20is%20concerned%2C%20all%20the%20pillars%20of%20democratic%20state%2C%20constitutional%20institutions%20like%20the%20ED%2C%20CBI%2C%20IT%2C%20EC%20all%20are%20being%20controlled%20by%20the%20executive%20and%20the%20executive%20itself%20is%20restricted%20to%20one%20person.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20judiciary%20at%20various%20levels%20has%20been%20weakened%20by%20various%20mechanisms.%20There%20are%20numerous%20examples%20of%20this%3B%20one%20such%20being%20the%20detention%20of%20activist%20Umar%20Khaild%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fa-timeline-of-umar-khalids-bail-hearings%5C%22%3Erefusal%20to%20hear%20his%20bail%20plea%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20last%20four%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFreedom%20of%20expression%20is%20down%20in%20the%20dumps.%20With%20the%20mainstream%20media%20under%20the%20belt%20of%20pro-government%20corporate%2C%20it%20is%20the%20voice%20of%20the%20government%20which%20is%20broadcast%20through%20major%20TV%20channels%20and%20newspapers.%20The%20independent%20voices%20have%20limited%20space%20available%20to%20articulate%20their%20opinions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFreedom%20of%20expression%2C%20the%20major%20pillar%20of%20a%20democratic%20society%20has%20gone%20for%20a%20toss.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFreedom%20of%20Religion%20has%20been%20declining%20with%20many%20international%20indices.%20%E2%80%98India%20as%20a%20country%20of%20particular%20concern%2C%E2%80%99%20is%20the%20label%20for%20India%20as%20per%20US%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fdesignate-india-as-country-of-particular-concern-us-religious-freedom-watchdog-9071092%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efreedom%20of%20religion%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20watchdog.%20As%20per%20V-Dem%2C%20India%20ranked%20104%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Findia-ranked-104-between-niger-and-ivory-coast-on-the-liberal-democracy-index-report%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20its%20democracy%20index%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20between%20Niger%20and%20Ivory%20Coast!%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20this%20isn%E2%80%99t%20unique%20to%20the%20BJP-RSS%20combine.%20Every%20%E2%80%98religious%20nationalist%E2%80%99%20outfit%20is%20averse%20to%20democratic%20freedoms%20and%20they%20resort%20to%20tuning%20their%20constitutions%20in%20such%20a%20direction.%20India%20is%20simply%20joining%20this%20club%20of%20%E2%80%98democracy%20suppressors%E2%80%99%20like%20Pakistan%20or%20Sri%20Lanka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20long%20ago%2C%20it%20was%20Lal%20Krishna%20Advani%20who%20had%20said%20that%20India%20is%20living%20through%20an%20undeclared%20emergency.%20All%20the%20components%20of%20democracy%20have%20been%20stifled%20through%20foot%20soldiers%20of%20Hindu%20nationalists%20and%20state%20officials%20while%20the%20government%20merrily%20looks%20the%20other%20way.%20It%20is%20a%20clear%20signal%20to%20these%20elements%20that%20this%20regime%20grants%20full%20impunity%20to%20violations%20of%20democratic%20rights%20of%20minorities%20and%20weaker%20sections%20of%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fram-puniyani%5C%22%3ERam%20Puniyani%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20president%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Study%20of%20Society%20and%20Secularism.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%