on%20or%20primary%20is%20held%20where%20voters%20decide%20the%20number%20of%20delegates%20each%20party%20convention%20receives%20and%20these%20delegates%20in%20turn%20select%20the%20party's%20presidential%20nominee.%20In%20primaries%2C%20candidates%20need%20a%20majority%20of%20delegate%20votes%20at%20the%20convention%20to%20win%20the%20party's%20presidential%20nomination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVoters%20now%20have%20a%20choice%20to%20make%20about%20the%20future%20of%20this%20country.%20Are%20we%20going%20to%20stand%20up%20and%20defend%20our%20democracy%20or%20let%20others%20tear%20it%20down%3F%20Will%20we%20restore%20the%20right%20to%20choose%20and%20protect%20our%20freedoms%20or%20let%20extremists%20take%20them%20away%3F%26quot%3B%20news%20agency%20Reuters%20quoted%20Mr%20Biden%20as%20saying%2C%20soon%20after%20the%20win.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3EBiden%20vs%20Trump%3A%20The%20Challenges%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2077-year-old%2C%20who%20is%20the%20first%20former%20US%20president%20to%20go%20on%20trial%20in%20a%20criminal%20case%20to%20hide%20hush%20money%20payments%20to%20a%20porn%20star%2C%20has%20been%20juggling%20court%20appearances%20while%20on%20the%20campaign%20trail.%20Mr%20Trump%20faces%2091%20felony%20counts%20on%20four%20indictments%20including%20attempting%20to%20overturn%20the%202020%20election.%20He%20is%20also%20the%20only%20American%20president%20to%20be%20impeached%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Biden's%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House%20has%20been%20obstructed%20by%20majority%20voters%20believing%20he%20is%20too%20old%20to%20serve%20another%20four-year%20term.%20The%20ongoing%20crisis%20at%20the%20US-Mexico%20border%2C%20where%20an%20influx%20of%20migrants%20has%20overwhelmed%20the%20system%2C%20is%20another%20weakness%20for%20the%2081-year-old%20leader.%20The%20recent%20murder%20of%20Georgia%20nursing%20student%20Laken%20Riley%20allegedly%20by%20an%20illegal%20immigrant%20has%20also%20become%20a%20flashpoint%20with%20the%20two%20parties.%3