India's%20culinary%20delights%2C%20the%20section%20for%20Delhi%20is%20uniquely%20beloved.%20From%20crisp%2C%20gooey%20sweets%20like%20jalebi%20to%20the%20tangy%20flavor%20of%20lamb%20pulao%2C%20the%20city%20is%20built%20around%20enjoying%2C%20sharing%2C%20defending%20-%20and%20bickering%20over%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELately%2C%20those%20passions%20have%20fixed%20on%20a%20single%20question%3A%20Can%20you%20trademark%20the%20world's%20most%20famous%20recipes%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20weeks%2C%20two%20popular%20establishments%20serving%20butter%20chicken%2C%20perhaps%20the%20most%20Delhi%20of%20Delhi's%20dishes%2C%20have%20been%20in%20court%20seeking%20clarity%20on%20the%20matter.%20The%20plaintiff%2C%20an%20old-school%20restaurant%20chain%20called%20Moti%20Mahal%20Delux%2C%20has%20argued%20in%202%2C752%20pages%20that%20its%20founder%20was%20the%20original%20inventor%20of%20butter%20chicken%20and%20therefore%20anybody%20who%20says%20otherwise%20is%20guilty%20of%20infringement.%20The%20defendant%2C%20a%20newer%20restaurant%20named%20Daryaganj%2C%20has%20countered%20by%20pointing%20out%20that%20it%2C%20too%2C%20has%20ancestral%20ties%20to%20another%20cook%20who%20claimed%20ownership%20of%20the%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20month%2C%20proceedings%20in%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%20will%20resume%2C%20with%20a%20major%20hearing%20scheduled%20for%20May.%20Managers%20at%20both%20restaurants%20have%20submitted%20newspaper%20clippings%2C%20archival%20photographs%20and%20food%20awards%20to%20back%20up%20their%20claims.%20Publicity%20from%20the%20case%20has%20been%20a%20financial%20and%20marketing%20boon%20for%20the%20chains%2C%20evoking%20nostalgia%20for%20the%20creamy%20chicken%20dish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20my%20family%20legacy%20that's%20in%20question%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Monish%20Gujral%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20Moti%20Mahal%20Delux.%20Gujral%20said%20his%20grandfather%20created%20butter%20chicken%20before%20Partition%20happened%20in%20the%201940s.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20personal%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20no%20minor%20lawsuit%20in%20Delhi%2C%20where%20bylanes%20are%20packed%20with%20vendors%20selling%20every%20kind%20of%20spice%2C%20the%20local%20tea%20seller%20is%20a%20neighborhood%20fixture%20and%20food%20is%20inscribed%20with%20centuries%20of%20culture.%20Many%20of%20the%20city's%20iconic%20dishes%20survived%20and%20evolved%20through%20generations%20of%20foreign%20rule%20and%20plunder.%20The%20tussle%20over%20butter%20chicken%20is%20about%20branding%20and%20business%2C%20but%20it%20also%20gestures%20at%20sacred%20preoccupations%20in%20India%2C%20where%20the%20origin%20of%20everything%20from%20the%20tunday%20kabab%20to%20rasgulla%2C%20a%20spongy%20dumpling%2C%20has%20come%20under%20similar%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20food%20culture%20took%20shape%20in%20the%201600s%20during%20the%20reign%20of%20Mughal%20emperor%20Shah%20Jahan%2C%20whose%20imperial%20kitchen%20housed%20cooks%20from%20Turkey%2C%20Iran%20and%20communities%20across%20South%20Asia.%20Spices%20served%20a%20practical%20purpose%20at%20the%20time.%20When%20a%20local%20hakim%2C%20or%20medicine%20man%2C%20found%20that%20many%20people%20were%20falling%20sick%20from%20polluted%20water%2C%20he%20suggested%20settling%20the%20stomach%20by%20adding%20lots%20of%20masala%2C%20ghee%20and%20yogurt%20to%20dishes%2C%20according%20to%20Salma%20Husain%2C%20an%20author%20and%20food%20historian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20British%20rule%2C%20India's%20palate%20tasted%20an%20explosion%20of%20new%20flavors.%20Migrants%20from%20Punjab%20brought%20tandoori%20cuisine%20to%20Delhi%2C%20using%20a%20large%20clay%20oven%2C%20sometimes%20buried%20in%20the%20ground%2C%20to%20cook%20poultry%2C%20vegetables%20and%20breads.%20Old%20Delhi%2C%20with%20its%20grand%20sandstone%20mosques%2C%20elegant%20havelis%20and%20thousands%20of%20hawker%20stands%2C%20became%20a%20laboratory%20for%20culinary%20experiments.%20Chefs%20added%20heavy%20creams%20to%20dry%20Mughlai%20meat%20dishes%2C%20concocting%20thick%2C%20flavorful%20curries.%20The%20variety%20drew%20visitors%20from%20across%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20city%2C%20Delhi%20is%20where%20the%20quest%20for%20food%20is%20fulfilled%2C%26quot%3B%20Husain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKundan%20Lal%20Gujral%20was%20among%20those%20to%20make%20Delhi%20home%20after%20the%20bloody%20period%20of%20Partition.%20A%20migrant%20from%20Peshawar%2C%20now%20part%20of%20Pakistan%2C%20Gujral%20and%20his%20business%20partners%20opened%20the%20original%20Moti%20Mahal%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20capital.%20As%20the%20story%20goes%2C%20Gujral%20created%20butter%20chicken%20to%20make%20use%20of%20leftover%20poultry.%20With%20his%20lambswool%20fez%20and%20signature%20mustache%2C%20he%20served%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20most%20famous%20people%2C%20including%20the%20Shah%20of%20Iran%20and%20Jacqueline%20Kennedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20question%20mark%20appeared%20over%20that%20narrative%20in%202019%20with%20the%20opening%20of%20Daryaganj.%20The%20restaurant%20chain%20was%20cofounded%20by%20the%20grandson%20of%20Kundan%20Lal%20Jaggi%2C%20a%20chef%20and%20business%20partner%20in%20the%20original%20Moti%20Mahal.%20Daryaganj's%20menus%20detail%20that%20chronology%20with%20an%20illustrated%20timeline%2C%20noting%20that%20butter%20chicken%20was%20invented%20after%20a%20large%20group%20of%20hungry%20customers%20showed%20up%20one%20evening.%20Jaggi%2C%20who%20was%20preparing%20to%20close%20the%20kitchen%2C%20improvised%20the%20recipe%20so%20his%20guests%20would%20have%20enough%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20right%20people%20should%20get%20the%20credit%20for%20what%20they%20started%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Amit%20Bagga%2C%20the%20chief%20executive%20of%20Daryaganj.%20He%20called%20trademarking%20such%20a%20widely%20adapted%20meal%20like%20butter%20chicken%20-%20and%20daal%20makhani%2C%20another%20staple%20claimed%20by%20Moti%20Mahal%20-%20%26quot%3Bpreposterous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20neighborhood%20where%20butter%20chicken%20was%20popularized%20is%20a%20tribute%20to%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20food%20nourishes%20the%20souls%20of%20Delhiites.%20In%20Chandni%20Chowk%2C%20a%20loud%2C%20labyrinthine%20shopping%20district%2C%20one%20street%20is%20devoted%20entirely%20to%20selling%20varieties%20of%20paratha%2C%20a%20flatbread.%20Every%20morning%2C%20scores%20of%20people%20from%20around%20Delhi%20line%20up%20at%20a%20single%20stall%20for%20a%20breakfast%20of%20chole%20bathure%2C%20spicy%20chickpeas%20served%20with%20puffy%2C%20deep-fried%20poori.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajeev%20Gupta%2C%20who%20conducts%20food%20tours%20in%20the%20area%2C%20said%20Delhi's%20restaurants%20are%20so%20firmly%20entrenched%20in%20their%20zip%20codes%20that%20they%20go%20out%20of%20their%20way%20to%20make%20a%20point%20of%20it.%20Take%20Jalebi%20Wala%2C%20a%20sweets%20vendor%20in%20Chandni%20Chowk%20that%20purports%20to%20have%20opened%20in%201884.%20%26quot%3BOLD%20FAMOUS%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20signage%20declares.%20%26quot%3BWE%20HAVE%20NO%20OTHER%20BRANCH%20IN%20DELHI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20neighborhood%20where%20butter%20chicken%20was%20popularized%20is%20a%20tribute%20to%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20food%20nourishes%20the%20souls%20of%20Delhiites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fight%20over%20butter%20chicken%20resonates%20because%20food%20is%20an%20identity%20here%2C%20Mr%20Gupta%20said%2C%20encompassing%20the%20reputation%20of%20a%20family%2C%20the%20memory%20of%20a%20painful%20migration%2C%20the%20start%20of%20a%20new%20life%20and%20the%20community%20that%20follows%20from%20sharing%20a%20hearty%20meal%20with%20those%20who%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20Delhi%2C%20it's%20not%20only%20about%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20about%20going%20together.%20Just%20for%20having%20a%20famous%20paratha%2C%20people%20are%20driving%2080%20kilometers.%20It's%20everything%20for%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710298260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fcmk7ga28_butter-chicken_625x300_24_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbutter-chicken-case-highlights-delhi-history-as-indias-culinary-capital-5228581%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20crisp%2C%20gooey%20sweets%20like%20jalebi%20to%20the%20tangy%20flavor%20of%20lamb%20pulao%2CDelhi%20is%20built%20around%20enjoying%2C%20sharing%2C%20defending%20-%20and%20bickering%20over%20food.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbutter-chicken-case-highlights-delhi-history-as-indias-culinary-capital-5228581%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbutter-chicken-case-highlights-delhi-history-as-indias-culinary-capital-5228581%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbutter-chicken-case-highlights-delhi-history-as-indias-culinary-capital-5228581%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Yami%20on%20being%20ok%20with%20Aditya%20not%20casting%20her%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710297450000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108448530%2Cimgsize-244741.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fyami-gautam-says-she-would-completely-understand-if-husband-aditya-dhar-did-not-cast-her-in-all-his-movies%2Farticleshow%2F108448525.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108448525.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EIn%20an%20industry%20known%20for%20its%20cutthroat%20competition%20and%20the%20strain%20it%20can%20place%20on%20personal%20relationships%2C%20navigating%20the%20world%20of%20showbiz%20together%20is%20no%20easy%20feat.%20Yet%2C%20Yami%20and%20Aditya%20have%20managed%20to%20do%20so%20with%20remarkable%20success.%20Yami%20said%20that%20this%20understanding%20has%20been%20present%20since%20the%20very%20beginning.%20She%20and%20Aditya%20have%20mutual%20trust%20in%20each%20other%2C%20both%20as%20individuals%20and%20professionals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fyami-gautam-says-she-would-completely-understand-if-husband-aditya-dhar-did-not-cast-her-in-all-his-movies%2Farticleshow%2F108448525.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Don't%20Play%20For%20India%2C%20State%20And%20Get%20In%20IPL%20Directly%3A%20Ex-MI%20Star%20On%20Pandya%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20season%20beckons%20and%20one%20of%20the%20most%20intriguing%20aspects%20of%20it%20will%20be%20the%20change%20of%20guard%20in%20Mumbai%20Indians.%20The%20five-time%20champions%20will%20have%20a%20new%20skipper%20at%20the%20helm%20in%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Hardik%20Pandya%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64177-hardik-himanshu-pandya-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHardik%20Pandya%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20with%20previous%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20featuring%20just%20as%20a%20batter.%20The%20move%20to%20change%20captaincy%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20debated%20topics%20in%20the%20buildup%20to%20the%20IPL%202024.%20Whether%20Hardik%20Pandya%20can%20lead%20his%20old%20franchise%20with%20success%20is%20the%20question.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%2C%20which%20has%20been%20widely%20shared%20on%20social%20media%2C%20former%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20player%20Praveen%20Kumar%20can%20be%20seen%20being%20asked%20this%20tough%20question%20on%C2%A0Mumbai%20Indians'%20change%20in%20captaincy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDid%20MI%20take%20a%20hurried%20decision%3F%20Or%2C%20the%20decision%20to%20make%20Hardik%20Pandya%20captain%20was%20the%20right%20one%3F%26quot%3B%20Praveen%20Kumar%2C%20who%20has%20played%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bangalore%2C%20Kings%20XI%20Punjab%2C%C2%A0%20was%20asked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20play%20two%20months%20before%2C%20you%20get%20injured%20two%20months%20before%20the%20IPL%2C%20you%20don't%20play%20for%20the%20country%2C%20you%20don't%20play%20for%20your%20state%20in%20domestic%20cricket%2C%20and%20just%20directly%20play%20in%20the%20IPL.%20That's%20not%20how%20things%20work.%20It's%20okay%20to%20earn%20money%2C%20who%20is%20stopping%20you%3F%20There's%20nothing%20wrong%20with%20that.%20But%20you%20have%20to%20play%20for%20state%20and%20country%20and%20now%20people%20only%20give%20importance%20to%20the%20IPL%26quot%3B%2C%20Praveen%20replied.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EFormer%20cricketer%20Praveen%20Kumar%20talking%20about%20Hardik%20Pandya%20how%20he's%20fit%20only%20for%20IPL%20but%20not%20for%20nation%20or%20domestic.%20He%20also%20feels%20Rohit%20Sharma%20could%20have%20captained%203-4%20more%20years%20in%20MI%20colour%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F2I6Hljvf88%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F2I6Hljvf88%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Immy%7C%7C%20%F0%9F%87%AE%F0%9F%87%B3%20(%40TotallyImro45)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTotallyImro45%2Fstatus%2F1767436727013290308%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2012%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20pacer%20advised%20young%20players%20to%20prioritise%20international%20cricket%20over%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20and%20try%20to%20balance%20both%20things%20in%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20saying%20this%20for%20long.%20Paisa%20kamao%2C%20kaun%20mana%20kar%20rha%20hai%3F%20Paisa%20kamane%20chahiye%20lekin%20aise%20bhi%20nahi%20hona%20chahiye%20ki%20aap%20domestic%20nahi%20khel%20rahe%2C%20country%20ko%20importance%20nahi%20de%20rahe.%20(Earn%20money%2C%20who%20is%20stopping%20you%3F%20But%20it%20shouldn't%20be%20like%20you%20are%20not%20playing%20for%20the%20country%20or%20domestic%20cricket).%20This%20thing%20is%20now%20firmly%20in%20the%20mind%20of%20players.%20Mai%20ek%20mahine%20pehle%20rest%20kar%20lunga%2C%20fir%20IPL%20khel%20lunga.%20Ye%20mentally%20hota%20hai%2C%20ki%20mai%20itne%20paise%20kaise%20chodun%20(Will%20rest%20for%20a%20month%20before%20the%20IPL%20and%20then%20play.%20This%20happens%20because%20mentally%20you%20are%20not%20willing%20to%20let%20go%20of%20that%20money).%20But%20this%20is%20not%20fair%20at%20all.%20A%20player%20needs%20to%20balance%20things.%20Money%20is%20important%2C%20but%20this%20(giving%20franchise%20cricket%20the%20priority)%20is%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20Praveen%20had%20told%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710297420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fh13ipcd8_hardik-pandya-_625x300_27_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fyou-dont-play-for-india-state-and-get-in-ipl-directly-angry-ex-mi-star-blasts-hardik-pandya-5226857%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai%20Indians%20will%20have%20a%20new%20skipper%20at%20the%20helm%20in%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20with%20previous%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20featuring%20just%20as%20a%20batter%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A68%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UTA%20Accused%20of%20Fraud%2C%20Breach%20of%20Contract%20by%20MediaLink%20CEO%20Michael%20Kassan%20(EXCLUSIVE)%2