or%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fafter-netflix-and-amazon-prime-video-apple-tv-may-get-a-cheaper-plan-with-ads%2Farticleshow%2F108443840.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BPM's%20Decision%20Is%20Right%26quot%3B%3A%20Smriti%20Irani%20Defends%20CAA%20Amid%20Protests%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20implement%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%202019%2C%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20government%20is%20%26quot%3Bcorrect%26quot%3B%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Smriti%20Irani%20said%20amid%20protests%20from%20opposition%20parties%20and%20claimed%20that%20the%20whole%20country%20supports%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20belonging%20to%20the%20Hindu%2C%20Sikh%2C%20and%20Jain%20communities%20from%20countries%20like%20Afghanistan%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20Bangladesh%20will%20be%20granted%20citizenship%2C%20a%20pledge%20fulfilled%20by%20PM%20Modi%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20speaking%20to%20the%20media%20in%20Bengal's%20Bardhaman%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMamata%20Banerjee%20(Bengal%20Chief%20Minister)%20will%20try%20to%20instigate%20a%20few%20communities%20for%20her%20vote%20bank%20but%20the%20whole%20of%20India%20knows%20this%20decision%20of%20PM%20Modi%20is%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Irani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20remarks%20come%20a%20day%20after%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20criticized%20the%20Modi%20government%20over%20the%20CAA%20notification%2C%20alleging%20that%20it%20was%20merely%20an%20election%20gimmick%20and%20that%20anyone%20applying%20for%20citizenship%20under%20CAA%20would%20be%20labeled%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Billegal%20migrant%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20central%20government%20implemented%20CAA%20yesterday.%20I%20am%20doubtful%20of%20its%20legality.%20There%20is%20no%20clarity%20from%20the%20government%20over%20this.%20This%20is%20a%20gimmick%20ahead%20of%20the%20elections.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20names%20of%2013%20lakh%20Hindu%20Bengalis%2C%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%2019%20lakh%2C%20were%20removed%20from%20the%20list%20in%20Assam%20in%20the%20name%20of%20NRC.%20Several%20people%20died%20by%20suicide%2C%26quot%3B%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20was%20linked%20to%20NRC%20and%20those%20who%20apply%20for%20CAA%20will%20immediately%20be%20considered%20illegal%20migrants%2C%20although%20they%20are%20citizens%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Ms%20Banerjee%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20BJP%20feels%20it%20has%20hit%20a%20sixer%20but%20it's%20a%20duck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20even%20one%20person%20gets%20it%20right%2C%20I%20will%20be%20happy.%20I%20will%20give%20protection%20to%20everyone.%20Do%20you%20know%20how%20many%20churches%20have%20been%20burnt%20in%20Manipur%3F%20Where%20were%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20when%20women%20were%20paraded%20naked%20in%20Manipur%3F%20Tell%20the%20truth%2C%20didn't%20you%20have%20Aadhaar%20cards%3F%20Do%20you%20have%20land%20and%20shops%3F%20The%20moment%20you%20apply%20for%20CAA%2C%20you%20become%20illegal%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%2011%2C%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20notified%20the%20rules%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%2C%20days%20ahead%20of%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20schedule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAA%20rules%2C%20introduced%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20and%20passed%20by%20Parliament%20in%202019%2C%20aim%20to%20confer%20Indian%20citizenship%20to%20persecuted%20non-Muslim%20migrants%20-%20Hindus%2C%20Sikhs%2C%20Jains%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Parsis%2C%20and%20Christians%20-%20who%20migrated%20from%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20and%20Afghanistan%20and%20arrived%20in%20India%20before%20December%2031%2C%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%2