Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20are%20required%20to%20purchase%20a%20lender's%20title%20insurance%20policy%2C%20which%20can%20be%20a%20significant%20out-of-pocket%20cost.%20The%20title%20acceptance%20pilot%20waives%20this%20cost%20for%20eligible%20refinance%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20currently%20a%20temporary%20program%20that%20is%20small%20in%20scope.%20Only%20borrowers%20who%20have%20more%20than%2020%25%20equity%20in%20their%20home%20and%20live%20in%20%26quot%3Bselect%20geographies%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20eligible%2C%20says%20the%20FHFA.%20It%20will%20also%20only%20be%20available%20on%20loans%20that%20have%20been%20deemed%20to%20have%20low%20title%20risk%20based%20on%20an%20automated%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Potential%20refinance%20closing%20cost%20savings%5C%22%3EPotential%20refinance%20closing%20cost%20savings%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20eligible%20for%20this%20program%2C%20how%20much%20you%20could%20save%20depends%20on%20how%20much%20a%20title%20insurance%20policy%20typically%20costs%20in%20your%20area.%20The%20average%20homeowner%20could%20save%20%24750%20on%20their%20closing%20costs%20thanks%20to%20this%20new%20program%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2024%2F03%2F07%2Ffact-sheet-president-biden-announces-plan-to-lower-housing-costs-for-working-families%2F%5C%22%3EWhite%20House%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20FHFA%20says%20that%20savings%20could%20range%20between%20%24300%20to%20%241%2C500.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Pushback%20from%20the%20mortgage%20industry%5C%22%3EPushback%20from%20the%20mortgage%20industry%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELeaders%20from%20the%20mortgage%20and%20title%20insurance%20industries%20overall%20weren't%20pleased%20with%20this%20announcement.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.alta.org%2Fnews-and-publications%2Fpress-release%2FALTA-Says-White-House-Attack-on-Title-Insurance-Offers-False-Promise-of-Savings%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Land%20Title%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bpurely%20political%20gesture%20offering%20a%20false%20promise%20of%20savings%20for%20homeowners%20while%20exposing%20consumers%2C%20lenders%2C%20and%20taxpayers%20to%20greater%20financial%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mba.org%2Fnews-and-research%2Fnewsroom%2Fnews%2F2024%2F03%2F07%2Fmba-statement-on-the-biden-administration-s-housing-affordability-initiatives-warns-against-cfpb-reforms-on-closing-costs-title-insurance%5C%22%3EMortgage%20Bankers%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bhas%20significant%20concerns%20that%20some%20of%20the%20proposals%20on%20closing%20costs%20and%20title%20insurance%20could%20undermine%20consumer%20protections%2C%20increase%20risk%2C%20and%20reduce%20competition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20if%20this%20pilot%20program%20could%20be%20continued%20or%20expanded%20down%20the%20road%2C%20particularly%20without%20industry%20buy-in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Closing%20costs%20remain%20a%20major%20hurdle%20for%20many%20borrowers%5C%22%3EClosing%20costs%20remain%20a%20major%20hurdle%20for%20many%20borrowers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20also%20announced%20during%20the%20State%20of%20the%20Union%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.consumerfinance.gov%2Fabout-us%2Fblog%2Fjunk-fees-are-driving-up-housing-costs-the-cfpb-wants-to-hear-from-you%2F%5C%22%3EConsumer%20Financial%20Protection%20Bureau%3C%2Fa%3E%20will%20be%20looking%20at%20ways%20to%20reduce%20closing%20costs%20for%20all%20mortgage%20borrowers%2C%20not%20just%20those%20who%20are%20refinancing.%20This%20will%20be%20especially%20beneficial%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-first-time-homebuyer-loans%5C%22%3Efirst-time%20homebuyers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20often%20have%20less%20cash%20saved%20up%20to%20bring%20to%20the%20closing%20table.%C2%A0%3C%2