hief%20Minister%20M%20L%20Khattar%2C%20he%20would%20also%20have%20been%20inducted%20in%20the%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20former%20home%20minister%20Vij%20had%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20BJP%20legislature%20party%20meeting%2C%20in%20which%20Mr%20Saini%20was%20elected%20as%20the%20leader%2C%20in%20a%20huff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20former%20chief%20minister%20Khattar%2C%20when%20asked%20whether%20Vij's%20name%20was%20there%20in%20the%20race%20for%20the%20post%20of%20a%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMinisters%20had%20to%20take%20oath%20today%20and%20his%20(Vij's)%20name%20was%20on%20that%20(list).%20But%20he%20could%20not%20come.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20whether%20Mr%20Vij%20was%20upset%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAnil%20Vij%20is%20our%20senior%20colleague...%20He%20sometimes%20gets%20upset%20easily%2C%20but%20he%20becomes%20normal%20later.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20past%20too%2C%20there%20have%20been%20many%20incidents%20when%20Mr%20Vij%20got%20upset%20over%20something%20but%20later%20on%20things%20were%20normal%2C%20said%20Mr%20Khattar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spoke%20with%20him.%20He%20said%20he%20did%20not%20feel%20like%20coming%20(for%20the%20oath-taking%20event).%20We%20will%20speak%20to%20him.%20Nayab%20Saini%20ji%20will%20also%20speak%20to%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Saini%20was%20sworn%20in%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20replacing%20BJP%20strongman%20Khattar.%20The%20development%20to%20bring%20in%20a%20new%20face%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20by%20the%20BJP%20came%20just%20weeks%20ahead%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khattar's%20second%20term%20as%20chief%20minister%20was%20to%20end%20in%20October%2C%20when%20the%20assembly%20polls%20are%20due.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vij%20was%20learnt%20to%20be%20upset%20as%20the%20party%20decided%20to%20elevate%20Mr%20Saini%2C%20ignoring%20the%20Ambala%20Cantt%20MLA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vij%20was%20not%20present%20at%20the%20oath-taking%20ceremony%20and%20after%20the%20BJP%20legislature%20meeting%20here%2C%20he%20headed%20straight%20to%20his%20Ambala%20residence%20in%20a%20private%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEmerging%20out%20of%20the%20BJP's%20meeting%20in%20Haryana%20Niwas%20before%20Mr%20Saini's%20oath-taking%20ceremony%2C%20when%20asked%20what%20transpired%20in%20the%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Vij%20evaded%20a%20direct%20reply%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Ebatane%20wale%20batayenge%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThose%20who%20have%20come%20from%20Delhi%20will%20tell%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Vij%20as%20he%20was%20seen%20leaving%20in%20a%20huff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20pictures%20from%20his%20Ambala%20Cantt%20residence%20showed%20him%20playing%20with%20a%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20in%202014%20too%2C%20when%20Mr%20Vij%20was%20among%20the%20frontrunners%20for%20the%20post%20of%20chief%20minister%20after%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20on%20its%20own%20strength%20in%20Haryana%2C%20the%20party%20chose%20first-time%20MLA%20Khattar%20for%20the%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vij%2C%20who%20also%20held%20the%20health%20portfolio%20in%20the%20outgoing%20Khattar%20cabinet%2C%20had%20in%20the%20past%20too%20expressed%20displeasure%20over%20many%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20months%20back%2C%20Mr%20Vij%20had%20expressed%20displeasure%20over%20interference%20in%20his%20department%20by%20officials%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20Office%20and%20has%20stopped%20clearing%20files%20for%20the%20last%20one%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20August%2C%20Mr%20Vij%20had%20denied%20having%20any%20intelligence%20input%20on%20a%20possible%20build-up%20of%20tension%20in%20Nuh%20which%20witnessed%20communal%20violence%2C%20and%20had%20said%20Khattar%20could%20give%20updates%20on%20the%20issue%20given%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Ball%20the%20information%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20after%20a%20tug-of-war%20with%20Khattar%20over%20the%20control%20of%20CID%2C%20Mr%20Vij%20was%20stripped%20of%20charge%20of%20the%20department%2C%20and%20was%20later%20allocated%20to%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vij%2C%20a%20six-time%20MLA%2C%20had%20then%20maintained%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20was%20supreme%20and%20he%20could%20take%20away%20or%20divide%20any%20department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20back%2C%20when%20Khattar%20expanded%20his%20cabinet%2C%20Vij%20was%20divested%20of%20the%20urban%20local%20bodies%20department%2C%20which%20was%20given%20to%20BJP's%20Hisar%20MLA%20Kamal%20Gupta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20February%202015%2C%20less%20than%20three%20months%20after%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20in%20Haryana%20for%20the%20first%20time%20on%20its%20own%2C%20Vij%20--%20who%20then%20held%20the%20health%20and%20sports%20departments%20--%20had%20taken%20a%20veiled%20dig%20at%20Khattar%20on%20X%2C%20posting%2C%20%26quot%3BThank%20you%20chief%20minister%20for%20taking%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20my%20departments.%20I'm%20relaxed.%26quot%3B%20Vij%20was%20then%20apparently%20upset%20with%20Khattar%20who%20had%20launched%20a%20number%20of%20programmes%20and%20schemes%20pertaining%20to%20departments%20handled%20by%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vij%20was%20among%20the%20frontrunners%20for%20the%20chief%20minister's%20post%20after%20the%20BJP's%20win%20in%20the%202014%20Haryana%20assembly%20polls.%20Mr%20Khattar%2C%20then%20a%20first-time%20MLA%2C%20had%20emerged%20as%20the%20party's%20choice%20for%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710268740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F60atssek_haryana-home-minister-anil-vij-ani_625x300_05_August_23.jpg%22%2C%2