%20are%20speculations%20that%20Mr%20Khattar%20may%20be%20asked%20to%20contest%20from%20Karnal%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Mr%20Khattar%20and%20all%2013%20other%20members%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20council%20of%20ministers%20submitted%20their%20resignations%20to%20the%20governor%20as%20a%20team%20of%20the%20party's%20central%20observers%20arrived%20in%20Chandigarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20switch%20in%20Haryana%20came%20amid%20the%20ruling%20BJP-JJP%20coalition%20coming%20apart%2C%20though%20party%20leaders%20from%20both%20sides%20did%20not%20make%20immediate%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20replaced%20Mr%20Khattar%20with%20OBC%20leader%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20who%20was%20later%20sworn%20in%20as%20Haryana's%20new%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khattar%20said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20happiness%20that%20youth%20face%20Mr%20Saini%2C%20an%20MP%20from%20Kurukshetra%2C%20was%20made%20the%20CM.%20He%20said%20Mr%20Saini%20is%20his%20old%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReplying%20to%20a%20question%2C%20Mr%20Khattar%20spoke%20about%20the%20JJP's%20demand%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20for%20the%20upcoming%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20BJP's%20target%20is%20to%20fight%20all%20the%2010%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Haryana%20and%20give%20them%20to%20%26quot%3BModi%20ji's%20kitty%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JJP%20must%20have%20spoken%20to%20the%20BJP's%20central%20leadership%20over%20this%20issue%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20he%20has%20come%20to%20know%20that%20the%20JJP%20has%20decided%20to%20contest%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20separately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20another%20question%2C%20Mr%20Khattar%20said%20it%20has%20been%20a%20tradition%20of%20the%20BJP%20to%20bring%20new%20leadership%20forward%20from%20time%20to%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20appointment%20of%20new%20chief%20ministers%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20are%20near%2C%20the%20parliamentary%20board%20decided%20to%20bring%20new%20leadership%20and%20Saini%20was%20chosen%20as%20the%20new%20leader.%20I%20am%20happy%20that%20new%20leadership%20has%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20that%20Tuesday's%20developments%20came%20a%20day%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20praised%20him%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Gurugram%2C%20Mr%20Khattar%20said%20he%20has%20old%20relations%20with%20the%20PM%20and%20that%20his%20appreciation%20has%20no%20connection%20with%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Khattar%20said%20sometime%20back%2C%20he%20himself%20had%20said%20that%20if%20any%20new%20leadership%20is%20to%20be%20brought%20in%20then%20it%20had%20to%20be%20done%20on%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20the%20expansion%20of%20Saini%20cabinet%2C%20Mr%20Khattar%20stated%20that%20it%20will%20soon%20take%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710260100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-10%2Fr63gh0mg_manohar-lal-khattar-ani-twitter-_625x300_14_October_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthink-its-possible-manohar-lal-khattar-on-contesting-lok-sabha-polls-5226286%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hours%20after%20he%20resigned%20as%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%20along%20with%20his%20cabinet%20ministers%2C%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar%20Tuesday%20hinted%20that%20he%20may%20be%20fielded%20by%20the%20party%20in%20the%20coming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fthink-its-possible-manohar-lal-khattar-on-contesting-lok-sabha-polls-5226286%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%