20and%20sentenced%20them%20to%20life%20imprisonment%2C%20lawyers%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQasim%2C%2045%2C%20was%20among%20the%20most%20prominent%20victims%20of%20state-induced%20hate%20crimes%20in%20the%20name%20of%20cow%20slaughter%20in%20UP%20after%20the%20infamous%20Dadri%20incident%20in%202015%2C%20when%20a%20Muslim%20man%20named%20Mohammad%20Akhlaque%20was%20beaten%20to%20death%20over%20rumours%20of%20killing%20a%20cow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQasim%20was%20beaten%20to%20death%20near%20the%20fields%20of%20Bajhera%20Khurd%20village%20under%20the%20Pilkhuwa%20police%20station%20in%20Hapur%20on%20June%2016%2C%202018%2C%20a%20year%20after%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%20and%20provided%20moral%20backing%20to%20violent%20cow%20protectionism%20and%20vigilantism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20accused%20in%20the%20Hapur%20lynching%20had%20even%20bragged%20about%20his%20role%20after%20he%20was%20released%20from%20jail%20on%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%E2%80%99%20families%20insisted%20that%20the%20allegations%20of%20cow%20slaughter%20were%20fabricated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20a%20detailed%20court%20judgment%20is%20still%20awaited%2C%20lawyers%20associated%20with%20the%20case%20said%20that%20ten%20accused%20persons%20were%20convicted%20for%20the%20crime%2C%20which%20had%20also%20left%20a%20Muslim%20farmer%20named%20Samaydeen%20badly%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12203719%2FVillage.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12203719%2FVillage.jpg%20840w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2