Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20alleged%20earlier%20that%20Vikramarka%20had%20%E2%80%98lost%20out%20his%20seat%E2%80%99%20next%20to%20Revanth%20Reddy%20during%20the%20temple%20rituals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20hit%20back%20saying%20that%20he%20was%20not%20the%20one%20to%20bow%20his%20head%20before%20anyone%20nor%20one%20to%20sit%20beside%20someone%20on%20one%E2%80%99s%20direction.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20said%2C%20he%20was%20not%20the%20one%20to%20kill%20his%20self-respect%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20pleasing%20others.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVikramarka%20recalled%20that%20he%20was%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20hierarchy%20in%20the%20state%20government%20as%20deputy%20chief%20minister.%20He%20said%20was%20proud%20of%20his%20place.%C2%A0Telling%20the%20public%20that%20the%20lapse%2C%20if%20any%2C%20was%20unintentional%2C%20he%20expressed%20solidarity%20with%20all%20those%20whose%20sentiments%20were%20hurt.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20attended%20the%20foundation%20stone-laying%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Singareni%20guest%20house%20in%20Banjara%20Hills%20in%20Hyderabad%20today%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ap7am.com%2Fen%2F76856%2Fbhatti-vikramarkas-take-on-the-yadadri-temple-seating-controversy%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhere%20he%20spoke%20about%20the%20comments%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20made%20against%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20arrival%20at%20the%20hilltop%20cave%20shrine%2C%20which%20is%2070%20km%20away%20from%20Hyderabad%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%20and%20his%20wife%20Geeta%20were%20given%20a%20warm%20welcome%20by%20temple%20priests%20and%20officials.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReddy%20was%20offered%20traditional%20silk%20robes%20to%20be%20presented%20to%20the%20deity%20and%20escorted%20to%20the%20sanctum%20sanctorum%2C%20which%20was%20reopened%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20six%20years%20due%20to%20renovations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWearing%20a%20turban%20and%20clad%20in%20a%20silk%20dhoti%2C%20Reddy%20sat%20on%20a%20low-level%20bench%20flanked%20by%20Ministers%20N.%20Uttam%20Kumar%20Reddy%20and%20Komatireddy%20Venkat%20Reddy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20melee%2C%20as%20priests%20chanted%20Vedic%20hymns%2C%20Vikramarka%20managed%20to%20get%20a%20seat%20but%20lower%20than%20the%20pedestal%20at%20the%20far%20end%20beside%20Komatireddy%20Venkat%20Reddy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20visuals%20%E2%80%93%20showing%20Vikramarka%20almost%20sitting%20on%20the%20floor%20and%20away%20from%20the%20chief%20minister%20%E2%80%93%20that%20hit%20social%20media%20invoked%20instant%20reactions%20from%20rival%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20alleged%20that%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20was%20given%20a%20raw%20deal%20because%20he%20belongs%20to%20a%20Scheduled%20Caste%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETelangana%20president%20of%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20R.S.%20Praveen%20Kumar%20demanded%20an%20apology%20from%20Revanth%20Reddy.%20He%20said%20the%20Congress%20had%20exposed%20its%20true%20colours%20by%20%E2%80%9Cinsulting%20the%20Dalit%20community%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVikramarka%E2%80%99s%20elder%20brother%20and%20senior%20vice-president%20of%20Telangana%20Congress%20committee%2C%20Mallu%20Ravi%2C%20said%20the%20party%20knew%20well%20how%20to%20treat%20Dalits.%20It%20made%20a%20Dalit%20person%20chief%20minister%20of%20erstwhile%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20in%20the%20past%20and%20now%20made%20a%20Dalit%20person%20a%20deputy%20chief%20minister%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20he%20recalled%20that%20the%20previous%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20government%20withdrew%20the%20leader%20of%20opposition%20status%20from%20Vikramarka%20by%20weaning%20away%20a%20sizable%20section%20of%20Congress%20MLAs%20and%20claiming%20a%20merger%20of%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20legislature%20party%20with%20that%20of%20the%20BRS%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%E2%80%99s%20previous%20term.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBRS%20leader%20and%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20SC%2FST%20commission%2C%20Yerrolla%20Srinivas%2C%20said%20the%20incident%20was%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20right%20in%20front%20of%20God.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20demanded%20a%20case%20be%20booked%20against%20those%20responsible%20under%20the%20SC%2FST%20(Prevention%20of%20Atrocities)%20Act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGeneral%20secretary%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20BJP%20unit%20G.%20Premender%20Reddy%20said%20it%20exposed%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20culture%20of%20ill%20treatment%20towards%20Dalits.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20hugged%20and%20honoured%20prominent%20Dalit%20leader%20Manda%20Krishna%20in%20full%20public%20view%20at%20a%20public%20meeting%20of%20the%20party%20in%20Hyderabad%20last%20year%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20showed%20how%20the%20BJP%20cared%20for%20the%20marginalised%20sections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFormer%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20and%20BRS%20MLC%2C%20K.%20Kavitha%2C%20said%20the%20incident%20exposed%20the%20social%20side%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20as%20he%20unveiled%20his%20intolerance%20towards%20the%20weaker%20sections%20one%20after%20another.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20also%20took%20exception%20to%20forests%20minister%20Konda%20Surekha%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20a%20backward%20class%20community%2C%20being%20given%20a%20shorter%20seat%20like%20Vikramarka%20at%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20row%20of%20VVIPs%20at%20the%20same%20ceremony.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EKavitha%20demanded%20an%20apology%20from%20Revanth%20Reddy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20secretary%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist)%20Tammineni%20Veerabhadram%20also%20demanded%20an%20inquiry%20as%20well%20as%20legal%20action%20against%20those%20who%20indulged%20in%20caste%20discrimination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20expressed%20anguish%20that%20the%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20and%20Konda%20Surekha%20%E2%80%93%20who%20also%20the%20holds%20endowments%20portfolio%20%E2%80%93%20were%20singled%20out%20for%20what%20he%20said%20was%20shabby%20treatment%20while%20the%20chief%20minister%20and%20added%20that%20two%20other%20ministers%20who%20sat%20next%20to%20him%20enjoyed%20the%20upper%20caste%20privileges%20bestowed%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeerabhadram%20also%20said%20that%20at%20least%20the%20other%20two%20ministers%20could%20have%20followed%20protocol%20and%20that%20it%20would%20have%20been%20a%20dignified%20gesture%20on%20their%20part%20if%20they%20had%20offered%20seats%20to%20Vikramarka%20and%20Surekha%20first%20and%20taken%20their%20own%20seats%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20incident%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20was%20alarming%2C%20he%20continued%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20state%20secretary%20K.%20Sambasiva%20Rao%20said%20the%20issue%20was%20being%20needlessly%20blown%20out%20of%20proportion.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERevanth%20Reddy%20had%20visited%20the%20temple%20to%20mark%20the%20inauguration%20of%20the%20eleven-day%20Brahmotsavams.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20temple%20was%20renovated%20by%20the%20BRS%20government%20at%20a%20cost%20of%20Rs%201%2C800%20crore%20and%20inaugurated%20by%20K.%20Chandrasekhar%20Rao%20two%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710252042000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F