22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fnasas-spacex-crew-leave-treats-behind-on-international-space-station-as-they-splash-down-after-months-in-orbit-13093206%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fnasas-spacex-crew-leave-treats-behind-on-international-space-station-as-they-splash-down-after-months-in-orbit-13093206%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fnasas-spacex-crew-leave-treats-behind-on-international-space-station-as-they-splash-down-after-months-in-orbit-13093206%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Heavy%20Rains%20Coupled%20With%20%26quot%3BPseudo-Development%26quot%3B%20And%20Govt%20Neglect%20Wrecks%20Havoc%20In%20Balochistan's%20Gwadar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12180043%2F429664226_726364946296535_389126-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKarachi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20the%20last%20week%20of%20February%2C%20Gwadar%20%E2%80%94%20a%20port%20city%20on%20the%20southwestern%20coast%20of%20Balochistan%20%E2%80%94%20was%20ravaged%20by%20heavy%20rains%20leading%20to%20widespread%20destruction.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1818078%5C%22%3Eauthorities%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%C2%A0%20the%20coastal%20town%20received%20180%20millimeters%20of%20rainfall%20over%20two%20days%20resulting%20in%20flooding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20were%20active%20to%20an%20extent%20only%20in%20the%20main%20city%20of%20Gwadar%20and%20in%20areas%20that%20were%20more%20affected%20such%20as%20Old%20Gwadar%20city%2C%20Jiwani%2C%20Pishukan%2C%20Surbandar%2C%20Palleri%2C%20Ganz%2C%20Kantani%2C%20and%20others%20where%20locals%20were%20living%20under%20the%20open%20sky.%20Affected%20people%2C%20however%2C%20had%20not%20been%20rescued%20and%20were%20left%20to%20manage%20on%20their%20own%20in%20other%20areas%20despite%20local%20administration%20declaring%20an%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Gwadar%20is%20often%20showcased%20as%20a%20developed%20city%20by%20the%20local%20Pakistani%20media.%20It%20is%20seen%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20changing%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20country.%20In%20a%20sharp%20contrast%2C%20the%20cries%20of%20the%20Balochs%20grew%20louder%20amidst%20the%20heavy%20rains%2C%20raising%20questions%20on%20who%20will%20change%20the%20fate%20of%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Mahrang%20Baloch%2C%20a%20prominent%20activist%20and%20leader%20of%20the%20Baloch%20Yakjehti%20Committee%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20two%20Gwadars%3A%20one%20portrayed%20by%20the%20Pakistani%20media%20as%20Dubai%20and%20Singapore%2C%20and%20another%20Gwadar%20where%20locals%20are%20submerged%20in%20rain-flood%20water%20and%20struggling%20for%20drinking%20water.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnderlining%20how%20the%20recent%20rains%20have%20devastated%20the%20lives%20of%20people%2C%20Dr.%20Mahrang%20noted%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Chouse%E2%80%9D%20means%20a%20single%20room%20in%20Gwadar%2C%20not%20the%20general%20definition%20of%20a%20house%20and%20it%20costs%20a%20huge%20amount%20to%20an%20individual%20to%20even%20construct%20and%20re-construct%20such%20a%20%E2%80%9Chouse%E2%80%9D%20when%20rain%20damages%20it%20repeatedly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20shelter%2C%20the%20ancient%20fishing%20community%20in%20the%20city%20has%20also%20been%20severely%20affected.%20Their%20boats%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lifeline%20for%20them%20as%20they%20rely%20on%20them%20for%20their%20livelihood%20%E2%80%94%20are%20damaged%2C%20each%20cost%20about%20Pakistani%20Rupee%2030%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTheir%20boats%20have%20been%20damaged%20and%20some%20of%20them%20swept%20away%20by%20heavy%20rains%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20affected%20fishermen%20to%20Mahrang.%20She%20continued%2C%20stating%20that%20if%20the%20local%20administration%20had%20announced%20a%20high%20alter%20and%20warned%20them%20strictly%2C%20the%20fishermen%20might%20have%20been%20able%20to%20save%20their%20boats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChina-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20is%20the%20real%20culprit%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20a%20devastating%20flood%20hit%20Pakistan%20which%20resulted%20in%20severe%20destruction%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Sindh%20and%20Balochistan%20provinces.%20Gwadar%20also%20witnessed%20torrential%20rains%20followed%20by%20flooding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20journalist%20Behram%20Baloch%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CRains%20or%20miseries%20are%20not%20first-time%20occurrences%20in%20the%20lives%20of%20Balochs%C2%A0%20nor%20are%20heavy%20rains%20new%20to%20Gwadar.%20Even%20in%202008%20and%202010%2C%20such%20rainstorms%20severally%20hit%20Gwadar.%20Ever%20since%20the%20government%20has%20not%20developed%20any%20infrastructure%20or%20drainage%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20most%20interesting%20point%20is%20that%20recent%20rains%20have%20badly%20exposed%20the%20state%20and%20its%20claims%20regarding%20development%20projects%20in%20Gwadar%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12180138%2F429809551_726381662961530_1517392007007355973_n.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12180138%2F429809551_726381662961530_1517392007007355973_n.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12180138%2F429809551_726381662961530_1517392007007355973_n-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12180138%2F429809551_726381662961530_1517392007007355973_n-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701333%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDr.%20Mahrang%20Baloch%20along%20with%20affected%20families%20in%20Gwadar.%20Photo%3A%20Baloch%20Yakjehti%20Committee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Mahrang%20went%20door%20to%20door%20to%20meet%20the%20affected%20people%20during%20the%20recent%20crisis.%20She%20explained%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpseudo-mega%20development%20projects%E2%80%9D%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20the%20ruin%20and%20destruction%20of%20the%20city.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20doubt%20that%20climate%20crisis%20is%20a%20reality%2C%20but%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20criminal%20negligence%20made%20it%20worse%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr.%20Mahrang%20underlined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20when%20she%20met%20the%20affected%20people%2C%20they%20told%20her%20that%20%E2%80%9Cit%20is%20Chine-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%20(CPEC)%20that%20has%20ruined%20our%20lives%2C%20stolen%20our%20employment%2C%20and%20now%20destroyed%20our%20homes.%20The%20rain%20has%20done%20less%20damage%20than%20CPEC.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Mahrang%20pointed%20out%20that%20infrastructure%20development%20has%20altered%20natural%20the%20drainage%20patterns%2C%20which%20previously%20facilitated%20the%20drainage%20of%20rain-flood%20water.%20Further%2C%20she%20asserted%20that%20these%20%E2%80%9Cpseudo%20projects%E2%80%9D%20have%20now%20obstructed%20natural%20pathways%20and%20have%20failed%20to%20assist%20in%20draining%20rain-flood%20water.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20some%20point%2C%20the%20locals%20even%20broke%20the%20roads%20to%20alleviate%20flooding%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGovernment%20is%20inactive%20and%20does%20not%20assist%20those%20who%20initiate%20the%20relief%20work%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20is%20less%20active%20in%20Gwadar%2C%20where%20a%20small%20number%20of%20locals%2C%20NGOs%20and%20other%20activists%20are%20voluntarily%20working%20in%20the%20city.%20It%20has%20also%20been%20reported%20that%20organisations%20like%20the%20Baloch%20Yakjehti%20Committee%20which%20are%20active%20in%20relief%20work%20are%20facing%20threats.%20The%20committee%E2%80%99s%20relief%20camp%20in%20Hub%2C%20a%20city%20of%20Balochistan%2C%20was%20removed%20and%20volunteers%20were%20warned%20not%20to%20continue%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20local%20administration%E2%80%99s%20presence%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20Dr.%20Mahrang%20mentioned%20that%20they%20had%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20seen%20them%E2%80%9D.%20She%20claimed%C2%A0%20that%20officials%20came%20and%20took%20pictures%20with%20generators%20to%20pretend%20that%20they%20were%20helping%20locals%20even%20when%20the%20localities%20only%C2%A0%20brought%20generators%20to%20pump%20out%20floodwater.%20The%20locals%20were%20afraid%20of%20speaking%20as%20they%20are%20under%20the%20scrutiny%20of%20military%20forces.%20%E2%80%9CLocals%20have%20been%20scrutinised%2C%20but%20no%20one%20is%20coming%20forward%20to%20help%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEchoing%20similar%20views%2C%20Behram%20said%20that%20the%20government%20is%20not%20active%20this%20time%20like%20how%20they%20remained%20inactive%20during%20the%202010%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20inactivity%20is%20part%20of%20a%20plan%20to%20compel%20locals%20to%20leave%20their%20land%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr.%20Mahrang%20stated%20that%20the%20torrential%20rains%20have%20revealed%20every%20unkind%20plan%20of%20the%20state%20towards%20Balochs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Gwadar%2C%20locals%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20leave%20their%20land%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20and%20even%20fishing%20community%20faces%20restrictions%20and%20is%20not%20allowed%20to%20fish%20freely.%20Now%2C%20the%20state%20remains%20silent%20and%20does%20not%20assist%20affected%20people%2C%20indicating%20that%20locals%20will%20ultimately%20be%20forced%20to%20abandon%20their%20land.%20She%20added%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwhen%20you%20lack%20shelter%20and%20protection%20for%20work%2C%20you%20are%20left%20with%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20make%20a%20difficult%20decision%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20a%20Gwadar%20where%20we%20can%20have%20two%20meals%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20affected%20people%20told%20Mahrang%2C%20she%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehram%20recalled%20an%20event%20during%20his%20reporting%20between%202004%20and%202005%20when%20official%20authorities%20were%20considering%20the%20relocation%20of%20entire%20local%20population%20to%20another%20place.%20However%2C%20this%20plan%20was%20later%20withheld%20due%20to%20the%20difficulty%20of%20relocating%20such%20a%20large%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20inactivity%20sends%20a%20clear%20message%20that%20they%20want%20locals%20to%20leave%20their%20land%20so%20they%20can%20install%20their%20mega%20projects%20in%20Gwadar%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFunds%20should%20be%20monitored%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1819513%2Fpm-unveils-relief-package-for-calamity-hit-gwadar%5C%22%3Evisited%3C%2Fa%3E%20rain-hit%20Gwadar%2C%20unveiling%20a%20relief%20package%20for%20affected%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20people%20do%20not%20need%20just%20a%20sack%20of%20wheat%2C%20or%20empty%20relief%20package%20announcements%2C%20%5Bthe%20government%5D%20assistance%20should%20aim%20to%20rebuild%20their%20lives%2C%20to%20provide%20them%20basic%20needs.%20But%2C%20politicians%20only%20show%20up%20when%20people%20are%20devastated%2C%20because%20we%20know%20what%20they%20have%20done%20in%20previous%20disasters%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Dr.%20Mahrang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20urged%20international%20communities%20to%20monitor%20funds%20being%20given%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20urged%20them%20to%20directly%20approach%20the%20affected%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710248456000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12180043%2F429664226_726364946296535_389126-1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fheavy-rains-coupled-with-pseudo-development-and-govt-neglect-wrecks-havoc-in-pakistans-gwadar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20Gwadar%2C%20locals%20have%20been%20forced%20to%20leave%20their%20land%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20and%20even%20fishing%20community%20faces%20restrictions%20and%20is%20not%20allowed%20to%20fish%20freely.%20Now%2C%20the%20state%20remains%20silent%20and%20does%20not%20assist%20affected%20people%2C%20indicating%20that%20locals%20will%20ultimately%20be%20forced%20to%20abandon%20their%20land.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fheavy-rains-coupled-with-pseudo-development-and-govt-neglect-wrecks-havoc-in-pakistans-gwadar%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Pehli%20Naukri%20Pakki'%20to%2030%20lakh%20Government%20Jobs%2C%20Congress%20Seizes%20the%20Right(s)%20Moment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F17182347%2F22.2.22-48.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20has%20announced%20five%20major%20policy%20proposals%20to%20tackle%20youth%20unemployment%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20power.%20Described%20as%20Yuva%20Nyay%20Guarantees%2C%20these%20include%20a%20clear%20timeline%20to%20fill%20vacant%20posts%20in%20the%20central%20government%3B%20a%20right%20to%20apprenticeship%2C%20gig%20workers%E2%80%99%20social%20security%2C%20a%20startup%20fund%2C%20and%20curbing%20exam%20paper%20leaks.%20The%20party%20has%20also%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20scrap%20the%20Agniveer%20Scheme%2C%20a%20four-year%20tour%20of%20duty%20contract%20for%20soldiers%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20array%20of%20promises%20and%20guarantees%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20reclaimed%20its%20%E2%80%98guarantee%E2%80%99%20space%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20tried%20to%20appropriate.%20Congress%20guarantees%20draw%20upon%20the%20guarantees%20promised%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Rajasthan.%20Most%20of%20them%20were%20legal%20guarantees%20quite%20different%20from%20BJP%20guarantees%2C%20which%20are%20more%20in%20the%20nature%20of%20commitments%20and%20assurances.%20While%20constantly%20mocking%20Congress%20guarantee%20schemes%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20state%20elections%20claiming%20that%20it%20would%20bankrupt%20the%20exchequer%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20quick%20to%20embrace%20the%20word%20guarantee%20after%20the%20Congress%20won%20the%20Karnataka%20elections.%20Congress%20guarantees%20contributed%2C%20at%20least%20partially%2C%20to%20its%20victory%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20also%20in%20Telangana.%20The%20BJP%20started%20using%20the%20term%20guarantee%20after%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20context%20for%20these%20proposals%20is%20the%20underwhelming%20economic%20performance%20of%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20government%20marked%20by%20its%20stark%20failure%20to%20address%20two%20related%20challenges.%20The%20first%20is%20the%20unequal%20distribution%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20rapid%20economic%20growth%2C%20which%20have%20accrued%20predominantly%20to%20the%20top%2010%25%20to%2020%25%20of%20income%20earners%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20economic%20inequality%2C%20has%20shown%20an%20alarming%20increase.%20The%20second%20challenge%20is%20high%20unemployment%2C%20which%20reached%20a%2045-year%20high%20in%202017.%20According%20to%20the%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20of%20Indian%20Economy%20(CMIE)%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20youth%20unemployment%20rate%20was%2045.4%25%20for%202022-23%2C%20six%20times%20higher%20than%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20overall%20unemployment%20rate%20of%207.5%25.%20The%20National%20Sample%20Survey%20Organisation%E2%80%99s%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20for%20July%E2%80%93September%202023%20showed%20that%20the%20unemployment%20rate%20for%20youth%20in%20urban%20India%20was%2017.3%25%2C%20three%20times%20higher%20than%20the%20official%20overall%20unemployment%20rate%20of%206.6%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECongress%20foregrounds%20unemployment%20and%20livelihood%20issues%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20proposals%20acknowledge%20the%20centrality%20of%20unemployment%20and%20joblessness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20issue%20has%20figured%20prominently%20in%20the%20second%20leg%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyaya%20Yatra.%20Given%20its%20timing%20and%20given%20its%20emphasis%20on%20Nyaya%20(justice)%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyaya%20Yatra%20would%20be%20assessed%20for%20its%20attempts%20to%20respond%20to%20specific%20political%20issues%2C%20and%20not%20just%20abstract%20rhetoric.%20The%20announcement%20of%20five%20guarantees%20is%20a%20step%20in%20that%20direction.%20The%20idea%20seems%20to%20be%20that%20governments%20can%20improve%20conditions%20of%20life%20and%20work%20for%20their%20citizens%20by%20providing%20employment%20and%20public%20services%2C%20which%20too%20can%20generate%20employment%2C%20and%20not%20just%20by%20simply%20distributing%20cash%20and%20rations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12175212%2FYouth_celeberating_National_Unemployment_Day_in_a_form_of_protest_-_Bank_Road_-_Prayagraj_Uttar_Pradesh_-_17_September_2020_-_01.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12175212%2FYouth_celeberating_National_Unemployment_Day_in_a_form_of_protest_-_Bank_Road_-_Prayagraj_Uttar_Pradesh_-_17_September_2020_-_01.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12175212%2FYouth_celeberating_National_Unemployment_Day_in_a_form_of_protest_-_Bank_Road_-_Prayagraj_Uttar_Pradesh_-_17_September_2020_-_01-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12175212%2FYouth_celeberating_National_Unemployment_Day_in_a_form_of_protest_-_Bank_Road_-_Prayagraj_Uttar_Pradesh_-_17_September_2020_-_01-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701320%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EOn%2017%20September%20Youth%20gathered%20to%20celebrate%20the%20birthday%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20as%20%E2%80%98National%20Unemployment%20Day%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20manner%20of%20protest%20against%20wrong%20policies%20of%20government%2C%20unemployment%20and%20contract%20system%20in%20jobs.%20Photo%3A%20Wikimedia%20Commons%2FPrajjwal3959%2FCC%20BY-SA%204.0%20DEED%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20central%20ideological%20plank%20of%20the%20Congress%20for%20the%202024%20elections%20is%20social%20justice.%20While%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Yatra%20raised%20the%20issues%20of%20political%20authoritarianism%20and%20socio-economic%20discrimination%2C%20its%20second%20edition%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20Nyaya%20Yatra%20is%20geared%20to%20achieve%20the%20constitutional%20ideals%20of%20political%2C%20social%20and%20economic%20justice.%20Political%20justice%20entails%20promoting%20the%20constitutional%20values%20of%20dignity%20and%20respect%20for%20all%20Indians%3B%20social%20justice%20involves%20participation%20of%20marginalised%20sections%20in%20decision-making%2C%20unity%20and%20harmony)%3B%20and%20economic%20justice%20entails%20a%20job%20for%20every%20Indian%20youth%2C%20and%20ending%20inequality.%20These%20are%20the%20key%20planks%20of%20this%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPehli%20Naukri%20Pakki%3C%2Fem%3E%20(first%20job%20guaranteed)%20which%20is%20the%20right%20to%20apprenticeship%20is%20an%20important%20guarantee%20to%20tackle%20unemployment.%20It%20will%20be%20like%20MGNREGA%20(Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act)%20that%20gave%20legally%20guaranteed%20employment%20to%20lakhs%20of%20people%20on%20demand%20in%20rural%20areas.%20The%20proposed%20Right%20to%20Apprenticeship%20law%2C%20will%20mandate%20private%20or%20public%20sector%20concerns%20to%20provide%20a%20one-year%20internship%20with%20part-government%20funding%20to%20any%20college%20degree%2Fdiploma%20holder%20on%20demand%20along%20with%20Rs%208500%20monthly%20stipend.%20This%20is%20for%20one%20year%20but%20it%20will%20provide%20skills%20that%20can%20facilitate%20employment%20in%20the%20future.%20Bharti%20Bharosa%2C%20a%20promise%20to%20fill%2030%20lakh%20vacancies%20in%20government%20sector%20jobs%2C%20is%20a%20really%20big%20guarantee.%20Another%203%20lakh%20jobs%20could%20be%20created%20in%20the%20education%20and%20health%20sectors%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20centrally%20sponsored%20schemes%20like%20Anganwadi%20and%20ASHA%20workers%20and%20the%20educational%20and%20health%20institutions%20of%20the%20central%20government.%20Then%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20proposal%20to%20establish%20a%20Rs.%205%2C000%20crore%20national%20fund%20to%20fund%20to%20youth%20across%20districts.%20People%20below%2040%20years%20of%20age%20will%20be%20able%20to%20avail%20of%20this%20fund.%20Promising%20a%20law%20for%20social%20security%20for%20gig%20workers%20such%20as%20drivers%2C%20guards%20and%20delivery%20boys%20is%20another%20important%20guarantee.%20On%20the%20issue%20of%20paper%20leaks%2C%20the%20Congress%20said%20it%20will%20standardise%20the%20government%20recruitment%20exam%20process%20and%20%E2%80%98stop%20its%20outsourcing%E2%80%99.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20promised%20a%20legally%20guaranteed%20Minimum%20Support%20Price%20(MSP).%20For%20the%20first%20time%20a%20national%20party%20has%20supported%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20legally%20guaranteed%20MSP%2C%20which%20is%20a%20guaranteed%20floor%20price%20for%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20produce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20called%20its%20promises%20as%20Congress%20guarantees%20but%20the%20BJP%20calls%20them%20Modi%20Guarantee%20or%20Modi%20Sarkar%20ki%20Guarantee.%20The%20latter%20are%20essentially%20government%20funded%20programmes%20and%20schemes%20across%20sectors%20which%20have%20been%20named%20and%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20renamed%20as%20Modi%20ki%20Guarantee.%20These%20guarantees%20depend%20for%20their%20implementation%20on%20trust%20in%20the%20leader%20or%20as%20the%20prime%20minister%20himself%20said%3A%20%E2%80%98people%20trust%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20guarantee%20because%20all%20other%20parties%20make%20false%20promises%E2%80%99.%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20guarantee%20means%20he%20alone%20could%20fulfill%20them.%20These%20are%20not%20legal%20guarantees%20or%20rights%2C%20they%20are%20assurances%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20to%20ease%20lives%20of%20people%2C%20business%2C%20and%20health%20etc.%20But%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20many%20of%20the%20economic%20promises%20made%20by%20this%20government%20over%20the%20past%20ten%20years%20remain%20unfulfilled%20as%20shown%20by%20status%20update%20of%20the%20major%20guarantees.%20The%20Congress%20on%20the%20other%20hand%20claims%20that%20more%20than%20four%20crore%20people%20have%20benefited%20from%20the%20successful%20implementation%20of%20guarantee%20schemes%20in%20Karnataka%20since%20the%20election%20of%20its%20government%20last%20summer.%20This%20will%20be%20its%20poll%20plank%20to%20counter%20the%20BJP%20in%20national%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20has%20foregrounded%20employment%20and%20livelihood%20as%20major%20issues%20in%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20for%20the%20general%20election.%20But%20much%20will%20depend%20on%20how%20these%20issues%20are%20communicated%20and%20whether%20the%20messages%20can%20reach%20people%20and%20whether%20it%20can%20surpass%20emotional%20issues%2C%20especially%20those%20surrounding%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20five%20guarantees%20will%20be%20evaluated%20for%20the%20political%20and%20electoral%20dividends%20rather%20they%20can%20yield%20than%20effectiveness%20as%20policy%20measures.%20But%20irrespective%20of%20outcomes%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20schemes%20are%20notable%20in%20terms%20of%20shifting%20public%20attention%20back%20on%20the%20urgency%20of%20policies%20to%20deal%20with%20unemployment%20and%20the%20problems%20of%20those%20facing%20distress%20and%20destitution.%20The%20basic%20principle%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20responsibility%20to%20guarantee%20all%20citizens%20a%20decent%20life%20and%20a%20minimum%20standard%20of%20living%20is%20one%20that%20definitely%20should%20be%20supported.%20In%20this%20sense%2C%20it%20goes%20beyond%20the%20immediate%20impact%20that%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20economic%20guarantees%20may%20have%20on%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%20What%20matters%20is%20the%20emphasis%20they%20give%20to%20education%2C%20health%20and%20employment%20%3Cem%3Eas%20rights%3C%2Fem%3E%20which%20can%20promote%20a%20deeper%20transformation%20of%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EZoya%20Hasan%20is%20Professor%20Emerita%2C%20Centre%20for%20Political%20Studies%2C%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru%20University.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710248342000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F09%2F17182347%2F22.2.22-48.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpehli-naukri-pakki-to-30-lakh-government-jobs-congress-seizes-the-rights-moment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress%20has%20reclaimed%20its%20%E2%80%98guarantee%E2%80%99%20space%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20tried%20to%20appropriate.%20Congress%20guarantees%20draw%20upon%20the%20guarantees%20it%20promised%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20Telangana%20and%20Rajasthan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpehli-naukri-pakki-to-30-lakh-government-jobs-congress-seizes-the-rights-moment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Contrasting%20Reactions%20to%20CAA%20in%20West%20Bengal%3A%20Matuas%20Celebrate%2C%20Rajbanshis%20Express%20Discontent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12171458%2FUntitled-design-38-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKolkata%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20implementation%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Act%20(CAA)%20has%20triggered%20varying%20reactions%20among%20communities%20across%20various%20districts%20of%20West%20Bengal.%20While%20Matua%20communities%20largely%20forming%20the%20Bangladeshi%20refugees%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20and%20Nadia%20are%20expressing%20relief%20and%20excitement%2C%20a%20starkly%20different%20picture%20emerges%20in%20North%20Bengal%2C%20particularly%20among%20the%20Rajbanshi%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20first%20public%20address%20after%20the%20CAA%20notification%2C%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20termed%20the%20CAA%20a%20divisional%20tactic%20to%20partition%20Bengal%20again.%20%E2%80%9CI%20will%20not%20allow%20anyone%20to%20become%20refugees%20again.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20bloodshed%20and%20people%20have%20come%20from%20Bangladesh.%20We%20are%20not%20accepting%20CAA.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20accept%20NRC%20and%20divisiveness%2C%E2%80%9D%20Banerjee%20said%20at%20a%20rally%20at%20Habra%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20one%20of%20the%20districts%20with%20significant%20Matua%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20second-largest%20Scheduled%20Caste%20group%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20constituting%203.8%25%20of%20the%20total%20population%2C%20the%20Matuas%20have%20persistently%20advocated%20for%20the%20proper%20rehabilitation%20of%20Hindu%20Bengali%20refugees%20from%20Bangladesh.%20In%202019%2C%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20secured%20victories%20in%20Matua-dominated%20seats%20like%20Ranaghat%20and%20Bangaon%20in%20Nadia%20and%20North%2024%20Parganas%2C%20while%20narrowly%20losing%20Krishnanagar%20to%20Trinamool%20Congress%20(TMC).%20However%2C%20in%20the%20recent%20Panchayat%20election%2C%20TMC%20recovered%20its%20lost%20ground%20winning%2049%20out%20of%20the%2053%20panchayats%20in%20these%20areas.%20The%20BJP%20won%20only%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20eyeing%20to%20consolidate%20the%20Matua%20support%20again%20to%20retain%20its%20two%20seats%2C%20seized%20the%20opportunity%20on%20Monday%20to%20capitalise%20on%20the%20recent%20announcement.%20In%20the%20Matua-dominated%20areas%20of%20Nadia%20and%20North%2024Parganas%2C%20the%20BJP%20workers%20organised%20celebratory%20events%20to%20commemorate%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20CAA%20as%20a%20political%20victory.%20Shantanu%20Thakur%2C%20the%20junior%20Union%20minister%20and%20head%20of%20All%20India%20Matua%20Mahasangha%2C%20hurried%20to%20the%20state%20BJP%20office%20in%20Calcutta%2C%20presenting%20packets%20of%20sweets%20to%20commemorate%20what%20he%20deemed%20a%20%E2%80%9Chistoric%20event.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20media%2C%20Thakur%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CHistory%20has%20been%20created%20today.%20A%20century%20from%20now%2C%20the%20government%20may%20change%2C%20but%20no%20one%20will%20ever%20question%20the%20citizenship%20of%20refugees.%20This%20is%20a%20response%20to%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20who%20spread%20misinformation%20and%20created%20unnecessary%20panic%20about%20the%20CAA%20jeopardising%20individuals%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20stay%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20strategically%20positioned%20itself%20as%20a%20champion%20of%20the%20interests%20of%20lower-caste%20Hindus%2C%20aiming%20to%20unite%20their%20votes.%20The%20party%20has%20successfully%20gained%20influence%20within%20West%20Bengal%E2%80%99s%20two%20significant%20Scheduled%20Caste%20communities%2C%20namely%20the%20Rajbanshi%20and%20Namashudra%20groups%2C%20collectively%20accounting%20for%2018.35%25%20and%2017.41%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20total%20Scheduled%20Caste.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDiscontent%20among%20Rajbanshis%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20North%20Bengal%2C%20the%20Rajbanshi%20community%2C%20asserting%20their%20indigenous%20status%2C%20vehemently%20opposes%20the%20CAA%2C%20demanding%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20National%20Register%20of%20Citizens%20(NRC)%20instead.%20The%20BJP%2C%20a%20dominant%20political%20force%20in%20the%20region%2C%20faces%20the%20challenge%20of%20mitigating%20discontent%20among%20the%20Rajbanshi%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBanshi%20Badan%20Barman%2C%20a%20prominent%20leader%20of%20the%20Rajbanshi%20community%20and%20chairman%20of%20the%20Rajbanshi%20Language%20Academy%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20CAA%2C%20we%20want%20NRC.%20If%20the%20government%20wants%20to%20enforce%20CAA%20here%2C%20it%20must%20first%20engage%20in%20dialogue%20with%20the%20people%20and%20take%20appropriate%20action.%20We%20want%20NRC%20with%20a%20cut-off%20date%20of%20March%2025%2C%201971.%20Rajbanshis%20are%20not%20ignorant%20anymore.%20We%20will%20only%20support%20those%20who%20address%20our%20interests.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20Roy%2C%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20Kamtapur%20Party%2C%20echoed%20this%20sentiment%2C%20expressing%20concern%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20protection%20for%20the%20Kamtapuri%20community.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20Kamtapuris%20are%20natives%20of%20this%20place%2C%20and%20we%20strongly%20oppose%20the%20way%20CAA%20has%20been%20introduced%20without%20providing%20us%20any%20protection%2C%E2%80%9D%20Roy%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajbanshis%2C%20making%20up%20around%2030%25%20of%20North%20Bengal%2C%20are%20the%20largest%20Scheduled%20Caste%20group%20in%20the%20state.%20For%20many%20years%20now%2C%20the%20community%20has%20been%20demanding%20territorial%20autonomy%20or%20separate%20statehood%20due%20to%20the%20perceived%20adverse%20effects%20of%20a%20significant%20influx%20of%20Bengali%20refugees%20from%20East%20Pakistan%2C%20resulting%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20land%2C%20economic%20opportunities%2C%20and%20cultural%20identity%20over%20the%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20won%20Cooch%20Behar%20and%20Jalpaiguri%2C%20both%20constituencies%20with%20over%2015%25%20Rajbanshi%20population.%20Rajbashis%20now%20find%20themselves%20disappointed%20and%20without%20the%20safeguards%20they%20had%20hoped%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharaja%20Anant%20Maharaj%20of%20the%20Rajbanshi%20community%2C%20a%20BJP%20Rajya%20Sabha%20member%2C%20had%20previously%20promised%20the%20creation%20of%20a%20Kamtapur%20union%20territory.%20However%2C%20he%20is%20yet%20to%20make%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA%2C%20he%20has%20fallen%20silent%20on%20the%20matter.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reached%20out%20to%20him%20for%20his%20reaction.%20The%20report%20will%20be%20updated%20as%20and%20when%20he%20responds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20CPI(M)%20minister%20criticised%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20approach%20as%20%E2%80%9Celection-centric%20drama%E2%80%9D%20and%20accused%20them%20of%20exploiting%20historical%20events%20to%20divide%20the%20people.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20is%20to%20deliberately%20sow%20confusion%20among%20the%20residents.%20They%20already%20vote%2C%20receive%20rations%20and%20pay%20taxes.%20What%20is%20the%20point%20of%20linking%20them%20to%20new%20citizenship%20policies%3F%20It%20reflects%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20divisive%20political%20approach.%20Should%20the%20citizenship%20of%20even%20one%20person%20be%20jeopardized%2C%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20take%20to%20the%20streets%20in%20protest.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESukhvilas%20Varma%2C%20former%20Congress%20MP%20of%20Cooch%20Behar%2C%20dismissed%20the%20CAA%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgimmick%E2%80%9D%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20playing%20a%20dangerous%20game%20of%20polarisation%20politics.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20claim%20that%20nobody%E2%80%99s%20citizenship%20will%20be%20revoked%2C%20but%20applicants%20must%20initiate%20the%20process%2C%20followed%20by%20providing%20documentary%20evidence.%20Now%2C%20the%20burden%20lies%20on%20the%20individual%20to%20prove%20that%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20leave%20their%20country%20due%20to%20religious%20reasons%2C%20subject%20to%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20judgment.%20The%20BJP%20has%20been%20engaging%20in%20polarisation%20politics%20for%20long.%20Even%20TMC%20was%20party%20to%20its%20original%20CAA%20200C%20policy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20the%20Bengali%20original%20by%20Aparna%20Bhattacharya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710246569000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12171458%2FUntitled-design-38-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcontrasting-reactions-to-caa-in-west-bengal-matuas-celebrate-rajbanshis-express-discontent%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20Matua%20communities%20largely%20forming%20the%20Bangladeshi%20refugees%20in%20North%2024%20Parganas%20and%20Nadia%20are%20expressing%20relief%20and%20excitement%2C%20a%20starkly%20different%20picture%20emerges%20in%20North%20Bengal%2C%20particularly%20among%20the%20Rajbanshi%20community.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcontrasting-reactions-to-caa-in-west-bengal-matuas-celebrate-rajbanshis-express-discontent%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Missing%20skiers%20tried%20to%20dig%20'snow%20caves'%20before%20they%20died%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710246480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F70x70%2Fskynews-cantonal-police-valais_6487963.jpg%3F20240312124322%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmissing-skiers-attempted-to-dig-snow-caves-before-death-in-swiss-alps-says-rescuer-13093181%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20group%20of%20skiers%20who%20went%20missing%20in%20the%20Swiss%20Alps%20tried%20to%20dig%20%26quot%3Bsnow%20caves%26quot%3B%20to%20save%20themselves%20from%20the%20freezing%20temperatures%2C%20a%20lead%20rescuer%20has%20told%20Sky%20News.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fmissing-skiers-attempted-to-dig-snow-caves-before-death-in-swiss-alps-says-rescuer-13093181%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmissing-skiers-attempted-to-dig-snow-caves-before-death-in-swiss-alps-says-rescuer-13093181%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fmissing-skiers-attempted-to-dig-snow-caves-before-death-in-swiss-alps-says-rescuer-13093181%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Haryana%3A%20With%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20as%20CM%2C%20BJP%20Banks%20on%20Non-Jat%20Votes%20to%20Retain%20Power%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12172628%2Fimage-1943-1.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChandigarh%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20By%20choosing%20its%20state%20unit%20chief%20and%20Kurukshetra%20MP%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20as%20the%20new%20Haryana%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20once%20again%20has%20banked%20on%20the%20consolidation%20of%20non-Jats%20to%20win%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20as%20well%20as%20retain%20power%20in%20the%20assembly%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaini%20belongs%20to%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBC)%20community%2C%20which%20makes%20up%20the%20largest%20share%20(40%25)%20of%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENayab%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20Saini%20caste%20alone%20makes%20up%208%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Saini%20driving%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%20the%20caste-centric%20politics%20of%20Haryana%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20party%20is%20focusing%20majorly%20on%20OBCs%20ahead%20of%20the%20polls%20to%20counter%20anti-incumbency%20from%20its%20previous%20government%20under%20Manohar%20Lal%20Khattar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20sign%20of%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20non-Jat%20consolidation%20came%20to%20the%20fore%20when%20it%20parted%20ways%20with%20the%20Jats-backed%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20(JJP)%20in%20the%20new%20government%20under%20Saini%2C%20which%20is%20primarily%20formed%20with%20support%20from%20independent%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20JJP%20MLAs%20may%20also%20defect%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20yet%20clear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JJP%20stayed%20in%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20under%20Khattar%20for%20four-and-a-half%20years%20before%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fharyana-cm-manohar-lal-khattar-resigns-amid-rift-between-bjp-jjp-alliance-over-seat-sharing%5C%22%3Eresigned%3C%2Fa%3E%20along%20with%20his%20cabinet%20on%20Tuesday%20(March%2012).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sudden%20move%2C%20though%20surprising%2C%20had%20been%20building%20up%20for%20several%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20suggest%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20not%20confident%20in%20replicating%20its%20electoral%20performance%20in%202019%2C%20when%20it%20secured%20ten%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20and%20later%20retained%20power%20with%20the%20JJP%E2%80%99s%20support%20in%20the%20assembly.its%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20changing%20its%20chief%20minister%20to%20an%20OBC%20face%2C%20the%20BJP%20thinks%20it%20will%20overcome%20the%20previous%20government%E2%80%99s%20challenges%2C%20especially%20when%20such%20an%20experiment%20has%20worked%20for%20it%20in%20states%20like%20Gujarat%20in%20the%20recent%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20learnt%20that%20Khattar%20was%20also%20part%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20non-Jat%20social%20engineering%2C%20but%20his%20growing%20unpopularity%20made%20it%20tough%20for%20the%20party%20to%20match%20its%20previous%20poll%20records.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPoll%20experts%20suggest%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Saini%20formula%20aims%20to%20ensure%20that%20non-Jats%20continue%20to%20support%20the%20party%20and%20that%20the%20leadership%20change%20is%20actually%20an%20excuse%20for%20course%20correction%20and%20intended%20to%20hide%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20past%20follies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20believe%20this%20may%20benefit%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20is%20leveraging%20the%20popularity%20of%20the%20Modi%20brand%20to%20sway%20voters%2C%20but%20that%20such%20gains%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%20later%20are%20not%20yet%20a%20done%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaryana%E2%80%99s%20caste%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20caste-centric%20politics%20of%20Haryana%2C%20Jats%2C%20comprising%20around%2025%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20have%20traditionally%20played%20a%20dominant%20role%20for%20decades%2C%20as%20other%20non-Jat%20communities%20either%20remained%20divided%20or%20aligned%20with%20the%20Jats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20non-Jat%20social%20engineering%20during%20the%20Modi%20era%20has%20altered%20the%20electoral%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Modi%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20seen%20only%20as%20a%20party%20of%20%E2%80%98upper%E2%80%99%20caste%20voters%20and%20urban%20voters%20in%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20changed%20under%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20after%20the%20party%20got%20a%20chunk%20of%20OBC%20and%20Dalit%20votes%20in%20addition%20to%20support%20from%20the%20Brahmins%2C%20Punjabi%20and%20Baniya%20communities%20both%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20as%20well%20as%20assembly%20polls%20since%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20analyst%20Vijay%20Chauhan%2C%20assistant%20professor%20at%20department%20of%20political%20science%20in%20the%20Maharana%20Pratap%20National%20College%2C%20Mullana%20(Ambala)%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Saini%E2%80%99s%20elevation%20is%20an%20extension%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20non-Jat%20politics%2C%20which%20continues%20to%20reward%20it%20politically.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20by%20elevating%20Saini%2C%20the%20BJP%20wants%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20repeats%20its%20performance%20in%20the%20last%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20when%20it%20won%20all%20ten%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20new%20government%20formation%2C%20Chauhan%20said%20that%20there%20is%20a%20strategy%20to%20divide%20the%20Jat%20vote%20bank%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jat%20vote%20bank%20in%20the%20state%20is%20largely%20divided%20between%20the%20Congress%2C%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD)%20and%20its%20splinter%20group%2C%20the%20JJP.%20By%20dumping%20the%20JJP%20and%20letting%20it%20fight%20alone%20in%20the%20upcoming%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20clearly%20trying%20to%20split%20Jat%20votes%20to%20its%20favour%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20if%20all%20Jat%20parties%20come%20on%20a%20common%20platform%20to%20stay%20in%2C%20fight%20or%20play%20on%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20terms%2C%20said%20Chauhan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20with%20a%20Gujarat-like%20change%20in%20leadership%2C%20the%20BJP%20also%20eyes%20electoral%20benefits%20beyond%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20learnt%20that%20the%20BJP%20changed%20the%20government%20in%20Gujarat%20months%20before%20the%20assembly%20polls.%20In%20Haryana%20too%2C%20it%20did%20the%20same%20thing%20with%20the%20hope%20that%20it%20retains%20power%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%20that%20are%20slated%20to%20take%20place%20soon%20after%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leaders%20are%20already%20claiming%20a%20clean%20sweep.%20Karnal%20BJP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Bhatia%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20party%20is%20confident%20of%20winning%20all%20ten%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20Haryana%20as%20well%20as%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20JJP%20state%20president%20Nishan%20Singh%20informed%20the%20media%20that%20a%20decision%20regarding%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20will%20be%20announced%20tomorrow%20during%20a%20rally%20in%20Hisar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESaini%20takes%20oath%20with%20independents%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20with%20support%20from%20independent%20candidates%2C%20Saini%20took%20oath%20as%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%2011th%20CM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20which%20currently%20has%2041%20MLAs%20in%20the%2090-member%20state%20assembly%2C%20needed%20the%20support%20of%20five%20more%20MLAs%20to%20retain%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20least%20five%20of%20six%20independent%20MLAs%20have%20already%20extended%20support%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20Sirsa%20MLA%20and%20president%20of%20the%20Haryana%20Lokhit%20Party%2C%20Gopal%20Kanda%2C%20also%20extended%20support%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20exchange%20for%20their%20loyalty%2C%20one%20independent%20MLA%2C%20Ranjit%20Singh%20took%20oath%20as%20minister%20along%20with%20other%20BJP%20leaders%20including%20Banwari%20Lal%2C%20Jai%20Parkash%20Dalal%2C%20Kanwar%20Pal%20Gujjar%20and%20Moolchand%20Sharma.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP%20accepted%20the%20moral%20defeat%20and%20Khattar%E2%80%99s%20failure%3A%20Congress%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20the%20media%2C%20Congress%20leader%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20Bhupinder%20Hooda%20said%20that%20by%20changing%20its%20chief%20minister%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20accepted%20its%20moral%20defeat%20besides%20the%20failure%20of%20its%20CM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20breaking%20of%20alliance%20with%20the%20JJP%20was%20not%20surprising.%20There%20was%20an%20agreement%20between%20these%20two%20%5BBJP%20and%20JJP%5D%20to%20break%20the%20alliance%20because%20this%20alliance%20has%20totally%20failed.%20This%20was%20not%20a%20policy-based%20alliance%2C%20it%20was%20a%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98thugbandhan%E2%80%99%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20people%20have%20realised%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710245716000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F12172628%2Fimage-1943-1.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fharyana-with-nayab-singh-saini-as-cm-bjp-banks-on-non-jat-votes-to-retain-power%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Another%20sign%20of%20the%20party's%20non-Jat%20consolidation%20came%20to%20the%20fore%20when%20it%20parted%20ways%20with%20the%20Jats-backed%20Jannayak%20Janta%20Party%20in%20the%20new%20government%20under%20Saini%2C%20which%20is%20primarily%20formed%20with%20independents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fharyana-with-nayab-singh-saini-as-cm-bjp-banks-on-non-jat-votes-to-retain-power%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ex-driver%20sues%20F1%2C%20Bernie%20Ecclestone%20and%20FIA%20over%20world%20champion%20claims%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%20%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%26nbsp%3B%20%26nbsp%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710245340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F03%2F768x432%2Fskynews-felipa-massa-f1-crashgate_6487939.jpg%3F20240312122951%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fex-ferrari-driver-sues-formula-one-bernie-ecclestone-and-fia-over-2008-world-champion-claims160-13093173%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Felipe%20Massa%20has%20taken%20legal%20action%20aga