20immediately.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20notice%20termed%20the%20%3Cem%3Ehartal%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20and%20unconstitutional%E2%80%9D%2C%20citing%20%E2%80%9Cvarious%20judgments%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Kerala%20high%20court%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Gauhati%20high%20court.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20this%20regard%2C%20your%20attention%20is%20drawn%20to%20the%20specific%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20honourable%20Gauhati%20High%20Court%20in%20writ%20petition%20%C2%A9%207570%2F2013%20dated%2019%20March%202019%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%20The%20legal%20notice%20also%20threatened%20that%20%E2%80%9Cin%20case%20there%20is%20any%20damage%20to%20public%2Fprivate%20property%20including%20railway%20and%20national%20highway%20properties%20or%20injury%C2%A0%20to%20any%20citizen%C2%A0%20caused%20due%20to%20%E2%80%98Sarbatmak%20Hartal%E2%80%99%2C%20legal%20action%E2%80%9D%20would%20be%20initiated.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20police%E2%80%99s%20notice%20is%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20state%20chief%20minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%E2%80%99s%20threat%20some%20days%20ago%20to%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20of%20Assam.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECiting%20the%20Gauhati%20high%20court%20order%2C%20he%20told%20reporters%20that%20if%20political%20parties%20call%20for%20a%20%3Cem%3Ebandh%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20protest%20implementation%20of%20the%20CAA%20in%20Assam%2C%20he%20would%20write%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20to%20deregister%20them.%20Sarma%20is%20also%20the%20state%20home%20minister.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReacting%20to%20the%20legal%20notice%20served%20by%20the%20state%20police%2C%20Akhil%20Gogoi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20undemocratic%20and%20dictatorial%20steps%20of%20government%20sets%20a%20bad%20precedent%20against%20the%20upholding%20of%20democratic%20culture%20in%20India.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20in%20anticipation%20of%20the%20MHA%20notifying%20the%20CAA%20before%20the%20general%20election%20dates%20are%20announced%2C%20the%20Sarma%20administration%2C%20since%20the%20last%20few%20days%2C%20have%20increased%20police%20presence%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Guwahati%20and%20several%20other%20cities%20and%20towns%20of%20the%20state.%20On%20March%2012%20morning%2C%20people%20noticed%20state%20police%20commandos%20marching%20on%20the%20city%20streets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETaking%20to%20X%2C%20state%20director%20general%20of%20police%20G.P.%20Singh%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAssam%20Police%20has%20made%20arrangements%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20one%20breaks%20any%20law.%20We%20are%20committed%20to%20protecting%20lives%20and%20property%20of%20residents%20of%20Assam%20from%20any%20kind%20of%20vandalism.%20Further%2C%20all%20laws%20and%20judicial%20pronouncements%20shall%20be%20fully%20implemented%20in%20accordance%20with%20laid%20down%20procedures.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20December%202019%2C%20when%20the%20CAA%20was%20passed%20in%20Parliament%2C%20the%20state%20witnessed%20massive%20public%20protests%2C%20including%20violence%20in%20Guwahati.%20Singh%20was%20at%20once%20dispatched%20to%20Assam%20by%20the%20MHA%20to%20take%20over%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20state.%20Hours%20after%20his%20takeover%2C%20five%20unarmed%20protesters%2C%20including%20a%2017-year-old%20boy%20were%20allegedly%20shot%20dead%20in%20Guwahati.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20July%202022%2C%20hearing%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20father%20of%20the%20boy%2C%20a%20local%20court%20in%20Guwahati%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fguwahati%2Fcourt-rejects-police-report-on-youths-death-in-caa-stir%2Farticleshow%2F92760733.cms%5C%22%3E%20refused%20to%20accept%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20state%20police%20report%20on%